<div class="container" id="formView">
    <div id="create">
        <div class="row m-bottom-30">
            <h1>Getting started</h1>

            <p>Let your gps file be analyzed is an easy process:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Choose one of the methods to analyze the file.</li>
                <li>Select your gps file.</li>
                <li>Click the start button.</li>
                <li>When the data is uploaded a map will be shown on which the analyzed track segments will be
                    displayed.
                </li>
                <li>By selecting the segments the transport mode can be changed.</li>
                <li>By clicking on the 'Finish'-button the track will be saved and cannot be changed anymore.</li>
            </ol>

            <div class="bs-component" id="errorForm" style="display:none">
                <div class="alert alert-dismissable alert-danger">
                    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert">Ã—</button>
                    <strong>The provided form data is not valid. You have to provide a valid analyzation
                        type and a valid gps file! The gps file should be standard conform and should use or at
                        least be valid according to the <i>"http://www.topografix.com/GPX/1/1" namespace.</i></strong>
                </div>
                <div id="source-button" class="btn btn-primary btn-xs" style="display: none;">&lt; &gt;</div>
            </div>

        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <form id="createForm" enctype="multipart/form-data" method="POST">
                <label>Select an analyzation method</label>

                <div class="form-group m-bottom-30">
                    <div class="radio">
                        <label>
                            <input type="radio" name="typeOptions" id="typeA" value="typeA" checked>
                            <b>Method A</b> - Analyze gps file by using only meta information calculated from
                            the
                            data.
                        </label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="radio disabled">
                        <label>
                            <input type="radio" name="typeOptions" id="typeB" value="typeB" disabled>
                            <b>Method B</b> - Analyze gps file by using not only meta information calculated
                            from
                            the
                            data in the file but also geografical information.
                        </label>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group m-bottom-30">
                    <label for="gpsFile">File input</label>
                    <input type="file" id="gpsFile">

                    <p class="help-block">Max file size should be below 10 megabyte.</p>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" id="createFormSubmit">Start</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
